OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1771931090
OL,3,CCosmetic reality TV star 'The Lip
OL,4,CKing' dies
OL,6,FThe man arrested over the UK's first
OL,7,Fliquid BBL death has died.
OL,9,FThe self-titled "Lip King", whose real
OL,10,Fname is Jordan James Parke, passed
OL,11,Faway last week.
OL,13,FParke was a beautician from the West
OL,14,FMidlands who appeared twice on the
OL,15,Freality TV show Botched.
OL,17,FHe told ITV's This Morning he was
OL,18,F"obsessed" with cosmetic surgery and
OL,19,Fhad had multiple procedures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
