OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1771931090
OL,3,CCosmetic reality TV star 'The Lip
OL,4,CKing' dies
OL,6,FTributes on social media say his
OL,7,Ffamily are "numb, shocked and
OL,8,Fheartbroken."
OL,10,FParke was arrested on suspicion of
OL,11,Fmanslaughter following the death of a
OL,12,Fwoman in 2024.
OL,14,FMum-of-five Alice Webb had the liquid
OL,15,For filler BBL in September that year.
OL,16,FShe became unwell during the procedure
OL,17,Fand was taken to Gloucestershire Royal
OL,18,FHospital, where she died.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
