OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1771931090
OL,3,CCosmetic reality TV star 'The Lip
OL,4,CKing' dies
OL,6,FParke was due to answer bail in March
OL,7,F2026. He was never charged with an
OL,8,Foffence.
OL,10,FA liquid BBL involves large quantities
OL,11,Fof cosmetic filler being injected into
OL,12,Fthe buttocks to make the bum look
OL,13,Fbigger.
OL,15,FUnder government proposals to regulate
OL,16,Fthe aesthetics industry, a filler BBL
OL,17,Fwould fall in the "red category" of
OL,18,Fthe most high-risk procedures.
OL,20,FThat means only a qualified healthcare
OL,21,Fprofessional can perform it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
