OL,3,CCosmetic reality TV star 'The Lip
OL,4,CKing' dies
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FMPs recognise that this would be a "de
OL,12,Ffacto ban" because of a "lack of
OL,13,Fappetite" amongst medical
OL,14,Fprofessionals to carry out the liquid
OL,15,FBBL.
OL,17,FAt the moment, though, there are no
OL,18,Flaws ruling who can or cannot legally
OL,19,Fprovide the procedure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
